{
  "stem": "10162.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, I hope to-- hope to live a long time because I feel I, I have so much to make up for.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I, I, I want to do so much more, and I have plans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm grateful that I was able to do at this age so much in the last 10 years, especially.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's, it's not particularly anything, because all through this, this political and racial and economical and personal upheaval, I always hung on to what I felt was the most important to me, like the, the beauty of the human spirit and the joy.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the-- and that's what-- that's what keeps giving a coherence to my every-- everyday life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some people, of course, look at my sculpture, and they say that they can see where I come from.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So maybe there is something there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have done-- I have done some work, like last year, I made this outdoor 'Tree of Life' menorah for this congregation on Long Island.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I have one Holocaust star subject sculpture at the Holocaust Center here in Nassau, at the Nassau County museum.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I have one plan, just one plan that I have for a Holocaust memorial that I have made a small maquette but I haven't translated into anything bigger.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe one day I will, which is-- which-- which is close to my-- close to my heart.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Other than that, nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The way the years go by, more and more, I get almost like sometimes like a panicky urgency to, to do something while I'm still here because there, there are less and less survivors.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we just don't know if there will be any in 10, 10 years or what.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
